Getting Started  with TypeScript and Node.js with the Installation of:

1-Node.js, 
2-TypeScript
3-VS Code on your computer.

1-Install Node.js
Download the Node.js installer from the official
website (https://nodejs.org/en) and run the
installer.

2-Install VS Code
Download VS Code from the official website
(https://code.visualstudio.com/download) and
install it

3-install typescript https://www.typescriptlang.org/download